text: Mathias Erang (1 May 1902 - 20 December 1978) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics, the 1928 Summer Olympics and the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1978 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saarland
